headline: GTA Online
subtitle: This Week’s Podium Vehicle: The Übermacht Zion Classic
content: Pay the lobby of The Diamond Casino & Resort a visit this week to give the Lucky Wheel a spin and walk away with pockets full of GTA$, RP, clothing, accessories, snacks, and other mystery prizes. This week’s top prize is the Übermacht Zion Classic, a German import beloved for its sleek silhouette.
